# ADVANCED SIGNAL RECONCILIATION SYSTEM
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 
# This trading bot uses an intelligent consensus engine to resolve conflicts
# between multiple signal sources:
#
# 1. HTF TREND (4H EMA/Structure) - Weight: 0.35
#    Most reliable long-term direction. Based on 4H candles with EMA ribbons
#    and structural analysis (HH/HL for bullish, LL/LH for bearish).
#
# 2. ML MODEL - Weight: 0.30
#    Predictive model signal with confidence score. Can suggest reversals
#    or support HTF direction.
#
# 3. S&R ZONE DETECTION - Weight: 0.20
#    30M supply/demand zone analysis. Identifies key support/resistance
#    levels and price action zones.
#
# 4. MARKET STRUCTURE (5M BOS) - Weight: 0.15
#    Break of Structure analysis on 5M. Detects momentum shifts and
#    structural reversals in lower timeframe.
#
# DECISION LOGIC:
# ─────────────────
# • Strong Consensus (conf >= 0.65, 3+ sources): TRADE with normal risk
# • Moderate Consensus (conf >= 0.55, no conflict): TRADE with normal risk
# • HTF-Dominant (HTF conf >= 0.6): TRADE with 60% risk reduction
# • ML Reversal (ML conf >= 0.75, decision conf >= 0.55): TRADE with 70% risk reduction
# • Low Consensus (conf < 0.55): SKIP - wait for better alignment
#
# CONFLICT RESOLUTION:
# ───────────────────
# When HTF trend and ML signal disagree:
#   - Assess divergence (how far apart the signals are)
#   - Low divergence (<0.1): Could still trade, use HTF as guide
#   - High divergence (>0.4): Significantly reduce position size (50%)
#   - ML reversal trades get special handling with reduced risk (70%)
#
# RISK ADJUSTMENT SCALING:
# ──────────────────────────
# Base risk = 0.5% per trade
# Low divergence (<0.1): 70% of base risk (high confidence setup)
# Moderate (<0.2): 85% of base risk
# Normal (<0.4): 100% of base risk
# High (>0.4): 50% of base risk (diversify or skip)
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 
# PROFESSIONAL SMC/ICT ENTRY SYSTEM (NEW)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# NEW FUNCTIONS ADDED (Lines ~940-1100):
# 
# 1. require_previous_extreme_sweep(price_data, direction, lookback=20)
#    → Confirms price swept previous LOW (BUY) or HIGH (SELL) for liquidity grab
#    → Returns: (swept: bool, sweep_level: float, swing_bar_index: int)
#
# 2. detect_fvg_retrace(price_data, direction, lookback=15)
