#    → Returns: (has_confirmation: bool, confirmation_type: str, strength: float)
#
# 4. execute_smc_entry_strict(symbol, price_data, direction, ..., require_sweep=True, require_retrace=True, require_micro=True)
#    → Master orchestrator: chains Sweep → BOS → Retrace → Micro in sequence
#    → Returns: (execute: bool, reason: str, confidence: float, details: dict)
