# 5. place_trade_with_smc_check(symbol, direction, lot, sl, tp, price_data=None, ..., enforce_smc=True)
#    → NEW WRAPPER: Runs SMC checks BEFORE place_trade() if enforce_smc=True
#    → Use this instead of place_trade() for institutional-grade entries
#    → Returns: Trade result or None if SMC checks fail
